The paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on entity linking using BERT, a popular language model. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning and neural networks, which suggests categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with optimization and performance evaluation, which could place it in categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
